            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "72歲米奇洛基Mickey Rourke𥄫女主持臀攬纖腰爆性騷擾 曾染毒癮打拳致腦震盪失憶失常",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"72歲米奇洛基Mickey Rourke𥄫女主持臀攬纖腰爆性騷擾 曾染酒癮毒癮打拳致腦震盪失憶失常\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/1b038c82daf95e8abfdd61ea5600548a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250409/_2025040914264840276.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">72歲米奇洛基Mickey Rourke𥄫女主持臀攬纖腰爆性騷擾 曾染酒癮毒癮打拳致腦震盪失憶失常</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>72歲荷里活男星米奇洛基（Mickey Rourke）最近參加英國知名真人騷《名人老大哥》（Celebrity Big Brother），但節目播出第一集，米奇已因為疑似性騷擾女主持而惹怒觀眾，他們紛紛在網上留言狂轟，更揚言要在觀眾投票環節中齊齊投票淘汰他。\n\n</p><h2>米奇洛基色瞇瞇行為怪異</h2>\n<p>事緣節目在周一晚上播出第一集時，兩位主持人Will Best和AJ Odudu介紹米奇出場時，米奇洛基一見到穿上繡滿閃石貼身服裝的AJ就表現熱情，乘機拉着人家跳舞，更讓AJ旋轉一圈，就將她拉到其懷中。接着又色瞇瞇地一直盯着AJ，更不斷看着她的屁股。AJ亦不禁以開玩笑的形式叫他別一直看着她，場面非常尷尬。及後AJ震驚得要平復心情，只能讓拍檔Will獨自訪問其他參賽嘉賓。節目出街後觀眾紛紛指責米奇，又揚言要投票盡早淘汰他出局。不過亦有部分網民則認為米奇在節目中表情怪異，並擔心其精神健康問題。除了疑似性騷擾女主持之外，他在與眾參賽嘉賓共住的房屋中亦神神化化，應該跟大家互動時，他忽然就攬住張被躺在沙發上睡覺。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185272/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"米奇洛基參加英國人氣真人騷《名人老大哥》，卻鬧出性騷擾爭議。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/349c0fca4683c4aa06e896a05f93931f/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_13_08_11.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        米奇洛基參加英國人氣真人騷《名人老大哥》，卻鬧出性騷擾爭議。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185273/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"米奇在周一晚上播出的節目中甫現身，就借機攬住女主持AJ Odudu。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/085a9e460f9d67385879313246d2e155/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_13_08_36.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        米奇在周一晚上播出的節目中甫現身，就借機攬住女主持AJ Odudu。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185274/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"米奇拉着AJ跳舞，並一個轉身就把人家拉進自己懷中。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eb4a5a71778220dbd21a2ef8640b5b10/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_13_09_07.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        米奇拉着AJ跳舞，並一個轉身就把人家拉進自己懷中。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185275/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"接着又一直上下打量AJ，甚至眼定定看着她的屁股。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3e7a85bd72967930ad7496cc84060096/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_13_09_48.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        接着又一直上下打量AJ，甚至眼定定看着她的屁股。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185276/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"AJ更半講笑半認真地叫米奇別一直看着她。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/14a3053269b67292d20f26a2a3df6a42/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_13_10_55.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        AJ更半講笑半認真地叫米奇別一直看着她。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185277/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"米奇在與其他嘉賓同住的房屋中，亦神神化化，忽然就攬住張被睡在沙發上。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/39f3daa4eceacd29f77f6973cb0b67ef/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_13_11_24.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        米奇在與其他嘉賓同住的房屋中，亦神神化化，忽然就攬住張被睡在沙發上。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185278/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"米奇曾發文自爆因在拳擊生涯中常遭受腦震盪，故此要做磁力共振檢查腦部。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b7c34156386c948d88010716622c13fa/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_13_11_49.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        米奇曾發文自爆因在拳擊生涯中常遭受腦震盪，故此要做磁力共振檢查腦部。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185279/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"他拍攝2008年電影《拼命戰羊》時服用類固醇，不但暴肥，更疑似造成情緒問題。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d472fddec1981ebeddddce62c07ef7ea/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_13_12_13.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        他拍攝2008年電影《拼命戰羊》時服用類固醇，不但暴肥，更疑似造成情緒問題。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185280/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"米奇是80年代荷里活性感偶像，與金碧辛加合演過經典情慾片《九個半星期》。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a686b847a9dc75decc24484a84462181/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_13_12_57.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        米奇是80年代荷里活性感偶像，與金碧辛加合演過經典情慾片《九個半星期》。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4185281/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"米奇與尊龍合演的黑幫電影《龍年》，亦是經典之作。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b08558fd979926c9745550bcca214fcb/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_13_13_33.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        米奇與尊龍合演的黑幫電影《龍年》，亦是經典之作。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>米奇洛基染酒癮毒癮</h2>\n<p>鑒於米奇洛基曾有染上酒癮和毒癮的黑歷史，加上成名前曾當業餘拳手的他在淡出影圈後又回歸拳壇，多年來在擂台上多次被打到腦震盪，他於2020年時就曾在社交網自爆要接受磁力共振檢查，檢查腦部，曾一度出現失憶徵象。此外，拳擊生涯又令米奇洛基經鼻子和顴骨骨折，曾多次接受整容手術。他為拍攝其金像提名作品《拼命戰羊》時，又曾服用類固醇健身，令他要花4、5年時間才解決過重問題。而類固醇戒斷後，亦有可能出疲勞、焦慮、抑鬱等情緒問題。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2062980/即時-娛樂-72歲米奇洛基Mickey-Rourke𥄫女主持臀攬纖腰爆性騷擾-曾染毒癮打拳致腦震盪失憶失常",
